# Google OAuth — create credentials at https://console.cloud.google.com
# APIs & Services → Credentials → Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application)
# Authorised redirect URIs:
#   http://localhost:3000/api/auth/google/callback   (local dev)
#   https://your-vercel-domain.vercel.app/api/auth/google/callback  (production)
